<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<meta name="description" content="A layout example that shows off a responsive product landing page.">

    <title>Landing Page &ndash; Layout Examples &ndash; Pure</title>

    
</head>
<body>
<div class="splash-container">
    <div class="splash">
        <img src="http://www.clipartbest.com/cliparts/y4T/9xa/y4T9xariE.jpeg">
    </div>
</div>

<div class="content-wrapper">
    <div class="content">
        <h2 class="content-head is-center">Reasons for existing</h2>

        <div class="pure-g">          
            <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">
                <h3 class="content-subhead">
                    <i class="fa fa-globe"></i>
                    Sports
                </h3>
                <p>
                    Find out when the Jets or Yankees are playing next, or prepare fo the next Mets playoff game. Distance coming soon!
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">
                <h3 class="content-subhead">
                    <i class="fa fa-music"></i>
                    Music
                </h3>
                <p>
                    Lots of cool stuff happening in New York. Tame Impala, Alabama Shakes, Modest Mouse are playing.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">
                <h3 class="content-subhead">
                    <i class="fa fa-gamepad"></i>
                    Video-Games
                </h3>
                <p>
                    Halo 5 , Fallout 4 , and Metal Gear solid 5 all in the same year. Take my money.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ribbon l-box-lrg pure-g">
        <div class="l-box-lrg is-center pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-2-5">
            <i class="fa fa-list fa-5x"></i>
            <i class="fa fa-calendar fa-5x"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-3-5">

            <h2 class="content-head content-head-ribbon">List or Calendar view.</h2>

            <p>
               Choose between a List or Calendar view. Get helpful informatoin such as days left, start time, location, and description. Visual cues to indicate type, show date order etc.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>




            <div class="l-box-lrg pure-u-1 pure-u-md-3-5">
                <h4>Contact Us</h4>
                <p>
			Come visit General Assembly at the back of the fourth floor!
                </p>

                <h4>More Information</h4>
                <p>
             	Project Three made by David Yoon, Neil Gewirtz , Swapnil Kasliwal, Thompson Crozier.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>


</div>


</body>
</html>
